{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1691-08_092","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Le Vieil Oiseau. Fable","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", août 1691 [tome 8], p. 92-96.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},"Je puis vous asseurer que les Vers qui suivent vous plairont, sans vous pouvoir dire le nom de l’Auteur. On m’a dit qu’ils sont d’un Gentilhomme fort jeune, qui ne fait pas profession d’estre Poëte. Son stile paroist fort aisé, &amp; le tour fin qu’il a donné à cette Piece, fait souhaiter d’en voir d’autres de sa façon."],"quote":{"label":{"#":{"value":"LE VIEIL OISEAU.","id":"/div/quote/label/#"},"lb":{},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"FABLE.","id":"/div/quote/label/hi/#"}}},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un vieux Rossignol de ce Bois","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Laissa femme jeune &amp; fringante.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aussi-tost d’Amans plus de trente,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Un chacun d’étaler sa voix.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" On ne vit onc Musique si charmante.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pas un ne plût pourtant, c’estoient","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Oiseaux de Cour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Lestes d’atour,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le col beau, la plume luisante,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Au surplus pas un sol de rente.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Belle aimoit l’argent, &amp; qui n’en avoit pas","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Estoit pour elle sans appas.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Tendres regards, douces paroles","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" N’y faisoient rien, il falloit des pistoles.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ce fut par là qu’en vint à bout","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Un riche Oiseau de ce Bocage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Riche je dis, car c’estoit tout.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Du reste vieux, de noir plumage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Oiseau d’un étrange jargon,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Car on dit qu’il parloit Gascon.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il n’était Femme un peu jolie","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Dans tous nos Bois,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  A qui cent fois","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  En son patois,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il n’eust conté son amoureuse envie.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  L’affreuse Pie","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Et la Fauvette tour à tour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Avoient écoûté son amour,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Sans en avoir l’ame attendrie ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais enfin il plaist en ce jour,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Et sans retour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Il se marie.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’affaire se conclut, dit-on,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Avant que le Printemps expire.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Tous les Oiseaux n’en font que rire,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et s’en vont chantant sur ce ton.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Quand on a l’âge","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De soixante ans,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Comme l’Oiseau du noir plumage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Plus de bon temps","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  En mariage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Le cocuage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  N’est pas le mal","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Le plus fatal ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ce qu’on doit craindre davantage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  En mariage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Quand on a l’âge","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De soixante ans,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Est d’aller voir en peu de temps","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Le noir rivage.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/#"}}]}}}}